data.description: Charming 3 bedroom / 2 bath, 1504 SF  single-story mid-century home in N. Yucaipa in quiet established neighborhood. Mountain views! No HOA! Low Tax rate! Great curb appeal. Handicapped accessible! New paint inside and out. Updated plumbing and electrical. Open and spacious floorplan. Lots of natural light. Remodeled in 2021.  Front porch, custom entry door. Some newer windows. New HVAC, Nest thermostat new roof. TV's  included. New vinyl plank floors and custom baseboards. Living room with custom ceiling fan. Open and bright remodeled kitchen with white cabinets, granite counters, custom lighting, graphite sink, stainless steel range, hood, and dishwasher. Indoor Laundry area. Large secondary bedrooms. Big Primary bedroom.  Custom / updated  bathrooms. Private backyard with large wooden patio cover, concrete patio, walkway. shed , and vegetable garden. Fig tree, lime tree, and peachtree. Great location! Close to schools, shopping and easy access to 10 Fwy.  DO NOT MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY!
